      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey quick question, i'm trying to figure out how to calculate my inventory turnover ratio for my clothing shop. also what does it actually mean if the ratio is pretty low?",
      "source": "evaluator",
      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "hey quick question, i'm trying to figure out how to calculate my inventory turnover ratio for my clothing shop. also what does it actually mean if the ratio is pretty low?",
